2026-05-10T17:30:51.1541904Z 21    <!--
2026-05-10T17:30:51.1542113Z 22        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-10T17:30:51.1542219Z 23        across Android versions:
2026-05-10T17:30:51.1542412Z 24          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-10T17:30:51.1542591Z 25            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-10T17:30:51.1542773Z 26            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-10T17:30:51.1542945Z 27          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
